original_title: Chikara Tag World Grand Prix 2008 - Night 1
overview: November 8th, 2008 :: The Tag World Grand Prix returns, this time in Oberhausen, Germany! Twelve teams battle not just for bragging rights, but also points towards a Campeonatos de Parejas title match! The team of Sha Samuels, Big Van Walter & Steve Douglas takes on the combination of Bad Bones, Emil Sitoci & Bernd Fohr. In a technical masterpiece, Mike Quackenbush takes on Johnny Saint, under "World of Sport" rules. The Tag World Grand Prix 2008 participates featured are Team Scotland, The Colony, The UnStable, Swiss Money Holding, The Osirian Portal, The Thrillers, F.I.S.T., Team Great Britain, Revolution Purple, and Team World Of Sport.
title: Chikara Tag World Grand Prix 2008 - Night 1
